name: Mercenary
description: With her past left in the dirt, she managed to slowly rise above her criminal rivals, making her name known for her ability to hack into the strongest security networks while being ruthless with her opponents. As her name went around in the streets, she found herself surrounded by more foes than friends, leaving many humbled before her mighty skills. However, she never did forget her original fate in the orphanage, always using the opportunities to help out the troubled and needy. Her eyes were set upon operating the worldâ€™s finest victimless criminal hacking syndicate, one that strives to break down massive despotic corporations to bring power back to the public, where it rightfully belongs.
